text: Very rude staff. Came at 9.45pm on 22/12/2024. We thought can still enter as the male staff at the door did not stop us but the female Malay cashier thought we didn’t understand Malay and sarcastically said “sudah tutup janganlah masuk. When we confronted her about it she just avoided the contact.

your staff so rude like no tutor?
Pls manager take attention

Good place to buy local product with lower price compare with Jaya Grocer.
You can find all basic necessities including some fresh vegetables, frozen meat, and pets food.
Nice place, has a wide variety of things you would find in a small mart and yet they are very competitively priced.
Well-stocked up and generally clean environment. Cashier can be a bit slow because they somehow only open one counter.
